@NODE I Introduction
	YAAE is an emulator for the swedish computer ABC80.
	

	Features:
	Fully coded in assembly language.
	Full ABC80 keyboard emulation.
	Full and FAST Z80 emulation with all undocumented instructions.
	Special HD0: device for fast file access.
@ENDNODE

@NODE R Requirements
	Requirements:
	* 68020+
	* OS 3.0+
	* 200k free RAM

	Recommended:
	* 68040
	* Fastmem
@ENDNODE


@NODE U Usage
	To start simply click the icon from Workbench or start from shell.
	To Quit press escape.
	To reset press F1.

	Preferences:
	All settings are made by tooltypes:
	FOREGROUND=rrggbb
	BACKGROUND=rrggbb
	FILEPATH=path
@ENDNODE
	
