@NODE K "Known Bugs"
	No sound emulation.
	Graphic bugs.
	Disk access don't work properly.
	The cursor in NTSC blinks to fast.
	All undocumented instructions of the Z80 does not work.
	It steals memory when started from the WB.
@ENDNODE

@NODE F Future
	Full sound emulation.
	Special Quick&Dirty mode for faster emulation.
	Faster, better.
	Normal ABC80 speed on 68030 50MHz
	A Z80 debugger
@ENDNODE
